score":93,"quote":{"pid":"420d0556711e63aeddd4accffc55071e9aae9790","tid":2106222,"uid":51064,"like":56,"dislike":5,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"7a66425e679313b1fa29400d92c0ed7edd518f03","tid":2106222,"uid":177789,"like":442,"dislike":3,"score":439,"citedBy":16,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:59:57.000Z","msg":"其中在黃金泳灘嬉水的泳客，被豬手打中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:02:12.000Z","msg":"睇到笑咗"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"游游下水 成隻豬手車埋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04d19d5e05fba8c9f1279ec3265b802d64a7247","tid":2106222,"uid":83378,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:03:51.000Z","msg":"大陸人趁洪水傾瀉上百噸豬內臟豬腳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2105035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2105035</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n飄左過黎姐 沒事"},{"pid":"21c1d80c49b22e2d9fe5aefe3307e6ad6418433c","tid":2106222,"uid":61589,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:04:11.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">中國新型豬流感 G4 據報已由豬傳人，佛奇：需嚴加關注</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/07/01/g4-ea-h1n1-attention/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F07%2F01%2Fg4-ea-h1n1-attention%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=07258a16\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/07/01/g4-ea-h1n1-attention/</a><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎（武漢肺炎、COVID-19）疫情未歇，<span class=\"red\">研究人員又在中國發現新型豬流感病毒</span>。美國白宮的新冠肺炎顧問佛奇（Anthony Fauci）指出，此一新病毒兼具 2009 年 H1N1 豬流感和 1918 年西班牙流感病毒的特徵，相當危險，必須嚴加關注。<br />\n<br />\nCNBC、紐約時報 6 月 30 日報導，中國發現的新型豬流感，名為「G4 EA H1N1」（簡稱 G4）。6 月 30 日美國國家過敏和傳染病研究所所長福奇在參議院聽證會上表示，G4 不是「立即威脅」，但是必須嚴加注意。福奇表示：「出現全新病毒變成大流行病時，通常是突變，或是基因重組和交換造成。」<br />\n<br />\n他說，G4 具備 2009 年 H1N1 病毒的特徵，也有 1918 年西班牙流感病毒的原始特徵。他警告，永遠有可能爆發另一場類似 2009 年的豬流感疫情。上述兩種病毒都相當致命，2009 年的 H1N1 豬流感，全球至少有 7 億人染疫，估計有 15.2 萬至 57.5 萬人死亡。1918 年西班牙流感導致 3 千萬至 5 千萬人死亡，殺傷力超越第一次世界大戰（2 千萬人死亡）。<br />\n<br />\n中國疾病預防控制中心、世衛組織（WHO）、中國數家大學、英國諾丁漢大學（University of Nottingham）共同研究，宣布發現 G4 病毒。英國動植物衛生機構（Animal and Plant Health Agency）病毒學部門主任 Ian Brown，審閱過該篇論文。Brown 說：「要是該病毒繼續改變，可能會對人類更具攻擊性，一如 SARS-CoV-2（新冠肺炎病毒）。」<br />\n<br />\n台大醫院兒童感染科主任黃立民（Li-Min Huang）強調，接下來需要探究是否有養豬場工作者遭人類傳染此一病毒，也需了解病毒是否傳播給養豬場工作者的家人。黃立民說：「這是非常重要的研究，該病毒看來相當危險。我們需要擔心任何有可能人傳人的疾病。」"},{"pid":"a5c8312dba6c5b0a16d145610fb45957a0bbfcb1","tid":2106222,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e8caf65ddb81d93004f291dac149f297c23e6ee3","tid":2106222,"uid":177789,"like":95,"dislike":2,"score":93,"quote":{"pid":"420d0556711e63aeddd4accffc55071e9aae9790","tid":2106222,"uid":51064,"like":56,"dislike":5,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"7a66425e679313b1fa29400d92c0ed7edd518f03","tid":2106222,"uid":177789,"like":442,"dislike":3,"score":439,"citedBy":16,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:59:57.000Z","msg":"其中在黃金泳灘嬉水的泳客，被豬手打中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:02:12.000Z","msg":"睇到笑咗"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"游游下水 成隻豬手車埋嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T08:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eed797b168d5aa19998