22.000Z","msg":"非洲豬瘟啲病豬係全屍，同埋人類都唔會感染非洲豬瘟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸長期靠香港走私凍肉解決肉食短缺問題，呢啲豬手九成九係香港附近水域啲走私客逃避水狗/海關嗰時跌咗落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f824427f67a9eba70c8dc46f86a1d4a80e634412","tid":2106222,"uid":346247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddcd94e188344242309f067798625bdf895f605d","tid":2106222,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T07:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8jd_ibxMfIfcQy4a6zIJr8ZBsVs=/543x249/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7YFDSDQGDQTYGVNHE35LZYLSQA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8jd_ibxMfIfcQy4a6zIJr8ZBsVs%3D%2F543x249%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7YFDSDQGDQTYGVNHE35LZYLSQA.jpg&h=f6eefddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屯門黃金泳灘及龍鼓灘石灘發現大量凍肉，包括發脹及發臭的豬手和雞翼在海中飄浮，其中在黃金泳灘嬉水的泳客，被豬手打中，嚇得失聲驚叫。有市民懷疑，這可能是上周五在內地虎門沙灘被廣泛發現的「漏網」豬手飄浮至港，也有人猜想會否是內地或本地走私凍肉船沉沒所致。泳客則擔心豬內可能帶有病菌甚至非洲豬瘟病毒，害怕泳灘會被污染致影響人體，故憂心忡忡。<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200713/R362AQHDNTFY4T5NCAQDNB3B4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200713%2FR362AQHDNTFY4T5NCAQDNB3B4M%2F&d=luXbQZY1AauiUI8MFdBmxFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=d27547f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200713%2FR362AQHDNTFY4T5NCAQDNB3B4M%2F&h=ea6577bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200713/R362AQHDNTFY4T5NCAQDNB3B4M/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T09:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi